{"tid":459503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屋企人都係好無公德心","createTime":"2017-11-05T19:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T02:49:44.000Z","uid":82899,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"10e6282a4316eea2e504b44276ab7efc18187b76","tid":459503,"uid":82899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:28:17.000Z","msg":"完全唔會做家務<br />\n由得啲衫堆到成座山咁<br />\n佢地唔會頂唔順 完全唔明咩心態<br />\n而我係有小小強逼症<br />\n一見到亂就頂唔順要執到好整齊 <br />\n所以最後屋企大部份家務都係我做都算<br />\n以前買過好多靚餐具翻黎一齊用<br />\n結果佢地係可以用到雙變單白變黃<br />\n完全無惜物慨念<br />\n最近買左兩隻玻璃杯 <br />\n我無奈到每次用完要收入衣櫃<br />\n結果今日唔記得收好其中一隻<br />\n就比屋企唔知邊個打爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有前日買左珪藻土地墊翻黎<br />\n寫埋大字叫佢地唔好著鞋踩<br />\n出左半日街 夜晚翻屋企<br />\n超多黑鞋印 <br />\n到左今日 佢地拎埋入浴室用<br />\n浸撚壞左塊嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想自己住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd71b3118632eeeb74eb2702c24cf4ab8df0705","tid":459503,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"肉醬多莉亞"},{"pid":"0a6e498f26ee6a81aae1d297ef69649d255a7d43","tid":459503,"uid":82899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肉醬多莉亞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76163a1cbdbf8f2235983e00338173aa09ad983","tid":459503,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:36:40.000Z","msg":"肉醬多莉亞"},{"pid":"08f1faaafadfc88ecbef21e58ee681fc5378af22","tid":459503,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:43:59.000Z","msg":"以為你講街外個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec3717e8c067298930ba2b59be70bc55edd86ac","tid":459503,"uid":82899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以為你講街外個種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對屋企都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都唔知佢地對外會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ecd806d78e5481a98fa9dfe454390d54aa70b93","tid":459503,"uid":82899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T19:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肉醬多莉亞</blockquote><br />\n咩事...."},{"pid":"3432d6879ca69ea773c95cf95e994fabc78a0e55","tid":459503,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T01:22:09.000Z","msg":"搬囉 咁多野講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無錢唯有硬食"},{"pid":"a3639d02ab7179d038cd3758d7cf259da966a1c0","tid":459503,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:40:15.000Z","msg":"佢哋似無腦多d"},{"pid":"931fe761251c419b45be47c337cf57165c0cf89c","tid":459503,"uid":113258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:49:44.000Z","msg":"著完啲衫亂咁放又唔洗<br />\n食完M記外賣、用過紙巾就咁放檯面<br />\n私自攞我啲衫褲鞋襪嚟著，用到污糟晒<br />\n夜晚偷雞唔刷牙把口臭死人<br />\n仲要同佢一間房<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}